Dubai, UAE
Posted on: 5 May 2014
THE ROLE
Expand all
Our client a leading holding group in Dubai is looking to hire a Receptionist Cum Secretary.
In this role you will provide support to the company and handle the reception area.
You will be responsible for diary management, correspondence, travel arrangements and all related administrative duties.
An Ideal person should have experience in manufacturing or Paint or chemical industry.
You will be entitled for a salary review after your probation period which will be calculated based on your Performance.
REQUIREMENTS
You must have at least 1-2 years experience working in a similar role in UAE/GCC
You should be organised, efficient and have a professional approach at all times.
You should be good Looking , smart & enthusiastic with a corporate approach.
This role is only open to candidates who can speak fluent Arabic.
Arabic nationals are only acceptable for this role.
Salary Upto 6000 AED (Full Package)
